\pard\f0\fs28 Rhizome with a perforated solenostele. Petiole with several vascular strands which fuse to form a single, U-shaped strand. Sori marginal, borne on the connecting veinlet, covered by both the deflexed margin of the leaf and by an inner indusium; spores tetrahedral.
